<p>I helped a new newspaper student publish this article on our school’s marine science club.
Although he was inexperienced and unfamiliar with many stylistic and grammar rules, he was eager to learn.
I enjoyed editing his writing and assisting him in transforming his draft into his first ever story.</p>
